## The non-negotiables

- Plan mode is required for changes touching more than 3 files, public APIs, refactors, or migrations. Draft via `context-engineer plan`.
- No placeholder comments. If you do not have enough context to implement something, ask.
- Use the project's package manager (`<pkg-mgr>`), not its alternatives. Lockfiles are committed.
- Run the fast verification after every meaningful change. Do not declare done until the full verification passes.

